name: Thrashervideo
0:
”Alexa, open skateboard bible”
”Alexa, ask the skateboard bible whats new”
”Alexa, ask skateboard bible whats playing on thrasher”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: skateboard bible
des: Now Alexa can help you check in on any new uploads to the Skateboard Bible(aka Thrasher Magazine). Just tell Alexa to ask Skateboard Bible what's new and she'll read you the title and descriptions of the latest videos.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
